### Create a note (requires login)
POST https://chase-pope-341.onrender.com/notes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Follow-up call",
  "body": "Need to call Carlos about the project proposal next week",
  "category": "work",
  "priority": "high",
  "contactId": "PASTE_CONTACT_ID_HERE",
  "dueDate": "2025-12-31",
  "completed": false
}

